RT::Extension::RSSFeeds
=======================

Add arbitrary RSS feeds to your dashboards

To install:
install to <plugin folder>/RT-Extension-RSSFeeds
Add "RT::Extension::RSSFeeds" to the @Plugins array in your RT_SiteConfig.pm

To use:
Click Logged in as <username>->Settings->RSS Feeds
Paste the feed URL, and check boxes to show the feed's title and/or image.
Click "Update RSS Feed" to preview the feed.
Select a privacy option, type a description, and click save.

Your saved RSS Feeds will now show up as available content in your MyRT or
dashboard edit pages.
